description:
Danny starts the show with a customer service story he needs to get off his chest. He then welcomes Becca Tobin (Glee/Ladygang Podcast) to talk all things #RHONY/Bravo, Glee, & more. Plus, hot takes on Carole's departure and part 1 of the Southern Charm reunion.


*For bonus episodes, join the Patreon @ Patreon.com/EverythingIconic
